{"tid":285444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一大班連登蝗蟲居然話垃圾中國菜好食","createTime":"2017-06-15T20:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T12:09:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":18,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4326c9bb9ed568057837fa80639bf69f869ec0c","tid":285444,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:41:50.000Z","msg":"我最鐘意就係食日餐，其次就係西餐，之後就係廣東菜。中國菜？！who care囉唔該！！老老實實，廣東菜我都唔係咁鐘意食架咋"},{"pid":"706e7dece8a2073c31ebf98ccdda93ebd73002e6","tid":285444,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:42:42.000Z","msg":"班友吹奏「中菜」呢個概念分明係大中華意識形態餘毒未清 <br />\n<br />\n之前我都鬧過幾次架啦 <br />\n<br />\n就算香港人其實都有好多唔同鄉下 <br />\n但我覺得都要識分返唔同菜派系 唔能夠將中菜一概而論 然後拎去比較話法意日都唔夠砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廣東菜=/=中國菜，唔唔好將高質廣東菜同蝗蟲菜相提並論</span></span>"},{"pid":"28e01c304d9b8528568500d709a18a158c34ce08","tid":285444,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:44:06.000Z","msg":"根本人種論上中國菜根本無可能做到世界前列，仲話要第一 <br />\n人地鬼佬日本佬做野認真程度根本無得比 ，中國人爆少陣炸都偷笑啦 <br />\n係，家常便飯的確唔錯多選擇，但做到藝術級別根本無可能 <br />\n宜家全世界都用日本／歐美牌子既科技有原因架，煮飯同一個邏輯"},{"pid":"696421e97afef9bd1e65701b0cc4373b7300d49a","tid":285444,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T20:51:17.000Z","msg":"要杜絕中國文化"},{"pid":"3ccdfe70f17b8dc980316558219cf4f8b9ae2924","tid":285444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b504e0bfb39e07368107e362e80df81899f34b0","tid":285444,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"啲負皮數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大中華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"